song.title: Once Upon A Quiver - Studiofied
song.info: Once Upon A Quiver was originally released as 32k executable track by myself at Kindergarden 2011. This new version, dubbed "Studiofied", is a complete rewrite from scratch :) Additional VST synths were used alongside quiver to give the song a brand new feel. 1st place in Pixeljam 2013 freestyle music competition.
